---
description: Tests — Jest unit and integration tests
globs:
  - src/**/*.test.*
  - src/**/*.spec.*
  - src/**/__tests__/**
  - src/**/__test__/**
---

Testing conventions:
- Jest with `ts-jest` and `@testing-library/react`
- Run: `npm test` or `npm test -- --watch`
- Mock `server-only` in test setup (see `jest.setup.js`)
- Tests live alongside source files or in `__tests__/` directories
- Focus on Services and utility functions
